## Feature support matrix

| Feature | PG | MySQL | MariaDB | Oracle | Trino |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| `$select` | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| `$filter` | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| `$orderby` | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| Pagination (`$count` + `$start_index`) | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| Safe params (`?col=val`) | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| Custom YAML queries | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| View definitions | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| JWT auth | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| Credential passthrough | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ (needs https) |
| DDL validation | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| Readiness probe (`/ready`) | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| Connection pooling | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ⚠️ no real pool — see Trino section above |

